---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Don Lim | Work Samples">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css" />

  <section class="page__content" itemprop="text">
    <article>
      <h2>R Programming</h2>
      <div class="work-samples-grid">
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h3>
            <a
              href="https://datacatalog.worldbank.org/search/dataset/0050771/global-database-on-intergenerational-mobility"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >World Bank - Global Database on Intergenerational Mobility (GDIM)</a
            >
          </h3>
          <p>
            Data analysis and visualization project using the World Bank's
            comprehensive dataset on intergenerational mobility across
            countries.
          </p>
          <div class="sample-links">
            <a
              href="/sample/Data-sample.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="sample-link primary">View R Analysis</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="techniques">
            <strong>Techniques:</strong> Clustering, choropleth visualization, OLS
            regression
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sample-card">
          <h3>
            <a
              href="https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/lakshmi25npathi/online-retail-dataset"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Retail Dataset II Analysis</a
            >
          </h3>
          <p>
            Comprehensive customer analytics on online retail data from Dr.
            Daqing Chen, London South Bank University.
          </p>
          <div class="sample-links">
            <a
              href="/sample/RFM_sample.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="sample-link primary">View R Analysis</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="techniques">
            <strong>Techniques:</strong> RFM analysis, heat maps, customer segmentation,
            clustering, retention and lifetime value analysis
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Python Programming</h2>

      <h3>Introduction to Data Science in Python</h3>
      <div class="work-samples-grid">
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/1 Intro to Data Science/Assignments/Assignment 1/assignment1.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Simple Regex</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Basic regular expression operations for text processing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/1 Intro to Data Science/Assignments/Assignment 2/assignment2.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Data Cleaning & Analysis</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Fundamental data cleaning and analysis techniques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/1 Intro to Data Science/Assignments/Assignment 3/assignment3.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Renewable Energy Analysis</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Data analysis of renewable energy indicators and trends.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/1 Intro to Data Science/Assignments/Assignment 4/assignment4.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Sports Analytics</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Correlation analysis of win/loss rates with population data from
            MLB, NBA, and NHL.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Applied Plotting, Charting & Data Representation in Python</h3>
      <div class="work-samples-grid">
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/2 Data Representation/Week 2/Assignment/Assignment2.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Temperature Records Visualization</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Visualization of record-breaking high and low temperatures in Ann
            Arbor (2015 data, 2005-2014 baseline).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Applied Machine Learning in Python</h3>
      <div class="work-samples-grid">
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/3 Applied Machine Learning/Week 1/Assignment/Assignment+1.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >KNN Classifier - Breast Cancer Dataset</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Training K-Nearest Neighbors classifier on sklearn's breast cancer
            dataset.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/3 Applied Machine Learning/Week 2/Assignment/Assignment+2.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >Multiple Classifiers - Mushroom Dataset</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Training decision tree, SVC, linear, and Lasso classifiers on UCI
            Mushroom dataset.
          </p>
          <div class="sample-links">
            <a
              href="http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Mushroom?ref=datanews.io"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="sample-link secondary">Dataset Source</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/3 Applied Machine Learning/Week 3/Assignment/Assignment+3.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Fraud Detection Analysis</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Training dummy and SVC classifiers on fraud detection data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/3 Applied Machine Learning/Week 4/Assignment/Assignment+4.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Blight Ticket Prediction</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Random forest classifier to predict blight ticket violations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Applied Text Mining in Python</h3>
      <div class="work-samples-grid">
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/4 Applied Text Mining/Week 1/Assignment/Assignment+1.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Datetime Processing</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Cleaning and sorting datetime data for text analysis.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/4 Applied Text Mining/Week 2/Assignment/Assignment+2.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Processing - Moby Dick</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Text parsing, lemmatization, and spell-checking analysis of Moby
            Dick.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/4 Applied Text Mining/Week 3/Assignment/Assignment+3.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Spam Detection Model</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Logistic regression and count vectorizer for spam message
            classification.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/4 Applied Text Mining/Week 4/Assignment+4.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Document Topic Classification</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Machine learning to compare document similarities and assign correct
            topics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Applied Social Network Analysis in Python</h3>
      <div class="work-samples-grid">
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/5 Applied Social Networks/Week 1/Assignment/assignment1.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Graph Creation & Manipulation</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Creating and manipulating graph structures and networks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/5 Applied Social Networks/Week 2/Assignment/assignment2.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Network Connectivity Analysis</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Analysis of network connectivity and graph properties.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/5 Applied Social Networks/Week 3/assignment3.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Centrality & PageRank Algorithms</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>Node centrality analysis, Scaled PageRank, and HITS algorithms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sample-card">
          <h4>
            <a
              href="/python/Coursera/5 Applied Social Networks/Week 4/Assignment/assignment4.html"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Link Prediction Model</a
            >
          </h4>
          <p>
            Logistic regression for predicting future connections (AUC: 0.935).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
